{"tid":2454053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"百業仆直 經濟重創 逾半受訪市民感悲觀","createTime":"2021-03-20T02:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-20T04:19:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e70ff5fd471a021486aabb61d1e9700323cd4749","tid":2454053,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T02:46:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/x6TGSonqezXkf6v5sbiQSA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NC44O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/oILylIQycw6AfNhUqPmioQ--~B/aD00Mjg7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/thesun.hk.com/13907b79c75dc51c29facfa862cc1832\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fx6TGSonqezXkf6v5sbiQSA--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NC44O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FoILylIQycw6AfNhUqPmioQ--~B%2FaD00Mjg7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F13907b79c75dc51c29facfa862cc1832&h=183e7edf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港民意研究所最新民意調查中，問到市民對本港未來經濟前景、政治環境及個人自由等的信心水平。結果顯示，超過一半受訪者對本港經濟前景冇信心，其中近三成人表示「好冇信心」；而表示有信心的市民比例不足四分之一。<br />\n<br />\n民主派支持者逾七成冇信心<br />\n<br />\n本港深陷疫情和財赤陰霾，經濟復甦無期下，庫房未來4年要繼續「見紅」。最新民調顯示，多達52%市民對本港經濟前景冇信心，當中有29%人表示「好冇信心」，23%人表示「幾冇信心」；而表示有信心者僅佔24%，表示「好有信心」的比例更低見5%。<br />\n<br />\n其中，民主派支持者「最睇淡」本港經濟前景，多達72%人直言冇信心，表示有信心者僅佔2%。而在非建制派陣營當中，雖然有四成人仍然對經濟前景有信心，但表示「好有信心」者亦不足一成；同時亦有接近四成非建制派支持者坦言冇信心，表示「好冇信心」的比例則超過一成半。<br />\n<br />\n此外，在政治環境方面，合計65%受訪者對此冇信心，表示有信心者僅25%；其中多達95%泛民人士表示冇信心，而非建制派表示有信心同冇信心的比率相若。至於港人未來享有的個人自由方面，合計64%人表示冇信心；民主派中多達93%人表示冇信心，而非建制派的看法亦維持兩極。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_9TOtFpFv5dJBscW0n6hLQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ni40O2NmPXdlYnA-/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/Sk1wlaC0LdmFnb2LDiOIDg--~B/aD00Mjk7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/thesun.hk.com/5580e94f4cd75a3eead39f0348c37e4d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_9TOtFpFv5dJBscW0n6hLQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4Ni40O2NmPXdlYnA-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FSk1wlaC0LdmFnb2LDiOIDg--~B%2FaD00Mjk7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F5580e94f4cd75a3eead39f0348c37e4d&h=8b4e2772&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2dd9050fcad1186a3cd5a619d8c248814cd84af9","tid":2454053,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:10:12.000Z","msg":"做呢啲民意調查算唔算觸犯國安法？"},{"pid":"374639c661e8c3afece11267afe8060dab84939c","tid":2454053,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c88abfb78df35e466dc69b78578ccdefcbc38b","tid":2454053,"uid":45324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:02:53.000Z","msg":"恆指仲二萬8喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5b1a8d8d41b29cd2323ff051a3736fb670746f","tid":2454053,"uid":393495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-20T04:19:48.000Z","msg":"點解係民主派 Vs 非建制嘅？睇唔明"}]}